A VALIUM, A SPECULUM,
WHATEVER, HUH ?

01:28:58.734 --> 01:29:01.737
WHATEVER.

01:29:01.737 --> 01:29:03.572
YOU LIKE BEING MRS. RANDONE.

01:29:03.572 --> 01:29:07.643
PROBABLY ALL
YOU'VE EVER KNOWN, HUH ?

01:29:10.513 --> 01:29:13.115
HAVE FUN IN FLORIDA.

01:29:26.862 --> 01:29:28.797
[ Door Shuts ]

01:29:41.844 --> 01:29:43.779
[ Chuckles ]

01:30:49.612 --> 01:30:53.482
* [ Ballad ]

01:30:53.482 --> 01:30:59.154
* WHY DO THESE EYES
OF MINE CRY *

01:31:00.222 --> 01:31:02.357
* DON'T THEY KNOW *

01:31:02.357 --> 01:31:04.593
* IT'S THE END *

01:31:04.593 --> 01:31:06.762
HAS SHE COME DOWN YET ?
* OF THE WORLD *

01:31:06.762 --> 01:31:09.464
NO.
* IT ENDED WHEN YOU SAID *

01:31:09.464 --> 01:31:13.201
BUT SHE'S BEEN PLAYING
THAT SHIT ALL MORNING.
* GOOD-BYE *

01:31:14.537 --> 01:31:17.272
* WHY DOES MY HEART *

01:31:17.272 --> 01:31:20.943
* GO ON BEATING *

01:31:20.943 --> 01:31:26.682
* WHY DO THESE EYES
OF MINE CRY *

01:31:28.216 --> 01:31:31.019
* DON'T THEY KNOW *

01:31:31.019 --> 01:31:34.422
* IT'S THE END OF THE WORLD *

01:31:34.422 --> 01:31:39.094
[ Knocks ]
DAISY ?
* IT ENDED WHEN YOU SAID *

01:31:39.094 --> 01:31:43.198
* GOOD-BYE **

01:31:49.371 --> 01:31:52.140
* [ Ends ]

01:31:56.278 --> 01:31:58.513
* [ Resumes ]

01:32:02.184 --> 01:32:04.787
* WHY DOES THE SUN *

01:32:04.787 --> 01:32:08.591
[ Meows ]
* GO ON SHINING *

01:32:08.591 --> 01:32:11.326
* WHY DOES THE SEA *

01:32:11.326 --> 01:32:15.463
* RUSH TO SHORE *

01:32:15.463 --> 01:32:18.466
* DON'T THEY KNOW *

01:32:18.466 --> 01:32:21.737
* IT'S THE END OF THE WORLD *

01:32:21.737 --> 01:32:25.473
* 'CAUSE YOU DON'T LOVE ME *

01:32:25.473 --> 01:32:29.211
* ANYMORE *

01:32:29.211 --> 01:32:32.014
* WHY DO THE BIRDS *

01:32:32.014 --> 01:32:34.282
DAISY ?
* GO ON SINGING *

01:32:35.884 --> 01:32:38.621
* WHY DO THE STARS *

01:32:38.621 --> 01:32:43.258
DAISY ?
* GLOW ABOVE *

01:32:43.258 --> 01:32:45.761
* DON'T THEY KNOW *

01:32:45.761 --> 01:32:49.031
[ Gasping ]
* IT'S THE END OF THE WORLD *

01:32:49.031 --> 01:32:52.668
[ Gagging ]
* IT ENDED WHEN I LOST *

01:32:52.668 --> 01:32:55.037
OH, MY GOD !
* YOUR LOVE **

01:32:57.305 --> 01:33:01.343
[ Sobbing ]
** [ Continues Indistinct ]

01:33:06.815 --> 01:33:08.951
OH,
WHAT AN IDIOT.

01:33:10.819 --> 01:33:13.355
** [ Continues ]

01:33:17.359 --> 01:33:19.561
[ Sobbing ]
YES, I NEED
AN AMBULANCE.

01:33:19.561 --> 01:33:21.697
MAKE IT A HEARSE.

01:33:21.697 --> 01:33:24.833
DAISY RANDONE.

01:33:24.833 --> 01:33:27.970
SHE KILLED HERSELF.

01:33:27.970 --> 01:33:31.606
TWENTY-THREE
VICAR STREET.

01:33:31.606 --> 01:33:34.743
YES.
PLEASE HURRY.

01:33:35.744 --> 01:33:37.880
* [ Continues ]

01:33:45.420 --> 01:33:46.755
YOU PRESSED HER BUTTONS.

01:33:46.755 --> 01:33:48.490
NOW YOU'RE TAKING HER MONEY.

01:33:48.490 --> 01:33:51.927
PLEASE. I DIDN'T PRESS SHIT.
SHE WAS WAITING FOR AN EXCUSE.

01:33:51.927 --> 01:33:54.663
COME ON, PACK UP.
WE HAVE TO GO. ALL RIGHT ?

01:33:54.663 --> 01:33:57.232
WE HAVE TO GO.

01:33:57.232 --> 01:33:59.167
WE HAVE MONEY.

01:34:02.705 --> 01:34:05.841
SUSANNA,
DON'T BE STUPID.

01:34:07.976 --> 01:34:11.780
ALL RIGHT, FINE.
BE STUPID.

01:34:11.780 --> 01:34:16.719
* IT ENDED WHEN YOU SAID *

01:34:16.719 --> 01:34:20.689
* GOOD-BYE **

01:34:20.689 --> 01:34:22.858
[ Sobbing ]

01:34:31.333 --> 01:34:33.335
[ Thunderclap ]

01:36:24.012 --> 01:36:27.415
WE SHOULD SEND SOMEONE
FOR A LITTER BOX.

01:36:44.366 --> 01:36:46.301
HEY.
HEY.

01:36:55.643 --> 01:36:57.645
CAN I--

01:36:57.645 --> 01:37:00.648
CAN I PET THE KITTY ?

01:37:00.648 --> 01:37:04.386
YEAH.
CAREFUL.

01:37:05.453 --> 01:37:07.455
HELLO.

01:37:07.455 --> 01:37:09.457
HELLO,
PUDDYCAT.

01:37:09.457 --> 01:37:11.459
KITTY.
[ Meows ]

01:37:11.459 --> 01:37:13.962
YOU'RE SO CUTE.

01:37:25.740 --> 01:37:27.876
[ Whispering ]
CHECKS.

01:37:29.477 --> 01:37:31.880
WHERE'S GEORGINA ?

01:37:31.880 --> 01:37:34.883
SHE'S STAYING
WITH POLLY TONIGHT.

01:37:34.883 --> 01:37:37.419
THEY'RE PLAYING
WITH YOUR CAT.

01:37:41.156 --> 01:37:43.291
DID THEY FIND LISA ?

01:37:44.759 --> 01:37:46.895
NO.

01:38:04.679 --> 01:38:07.349
I COULDN'T STAND UP TO HER.

01:38:11.219 --> 01:38:15.090
A DECENT PERSON
WOULD HAVE DONE SOMETHING.

01:38:17.425 --> 01:38:19.361
SHUT HER UP.

01:38:22.965 --> 01:38:25.100
GONE UPSTAIRS.

01:38:25.968 --> 01:38:28.103
TALKED TO DAISY.

01:38:30.705 --> 01:38:33.241
MELVIN SAID YOU WENT UPSTAIRS.

01:38:35.310 --> 01:38:37.245
TOO LATE.

01:38:39.381 --> 01:38:41.984
WHAT WOULD
YOU HAVE SAID TO HER ?

01:38:43.585 --> 01:38:45.520
I DON'T KNOW.

01:38:46.989 --> 01:38:49.524
THAT I WAS SORRY.

01:38:54.529 --> 01:38:58.266
THAT I'LL NEVER KNOW
WHAT IT WAS LIKE TO BE HER,

01:39:02.070 --> 01:39:06.341
BUT I KNOW WHAT IT'S LIKE
TO WANT TO DIE.

01:39:10.078 --> 01:39:12.947
HOW IT HURTS TO SMILE.

01:39:14.349 --> 01:39:18.086
HOW YOU TRY TO FIT IN,
BUT YOU CAN'T.

01:39:19.487 --> 01:39:23.091
HOW YOU HURT YOURSELF
ON THE OUTSIDE...

01:39:23.091 --> 01:39:26.628
TO TRY TO KILL THE THING
ON THE INSIDE.

01:39:28.563 --> 01:39:30.365
SUSANNA,

01:39:30.365 --> 01:39:33.168
IT'S ALL WELL AND GOOD
TO TELL ME ALL THIS,

01:39:33.168 --> 01:39:36.971
BUT YOU'VE GOT TO TELL
SOME OF THIS TO YOUR DOCTORS.

01:39:44.112 --> 01:39:46.114
HOW THE HELL AM I
SUPPOSED TO RECOVER...

01:39:46.114 --> 01:39:49.284
WHEN I DON'T EVEN
UNDERSTAND MY DISEASE ?

01:39:50.152 --> 01:39:52.520
BUT YOU DO UNDERSTAND IT.

01:39:52.520 --> 01:39:56.324
YOU SPOKE VERY CLEARLY
ABOUT IT A SECOND AGO.

01:39:56.324 --> 01:40:00.328
BUT I THINK
WHAT YOU'VE GOT TO DO
IS PUT IT DOWN.

01:40:00.328 --> 01:40:02.997
PUT IT AWAY.
PUT IT IN YOUR NOTEBOOK.

01:40:02.997 --> 01:40:05.200
BUT GET IT OUT OF YOURSELF--

01:40:05.200 --> 01:40:09.404
AWAY, SO YOU CAN'T
CURL UP WITH IT ANYMORE.

01:40:16.744 --> 01:40:19.781
LISA THINKS IT'S A GIFT.

01:40:21.883 --> 01:40:25.287
THAT IT LETS YOU SEE
THE TRUTH.

01:40:28.022 --> 01:40:31.726
LISA HAS BEEN HERE
FOR EIGHT YEARS.

01:40:38.433 --> 01:40:41.336
[ Sobbing ]
I'M SO SORRY.

01:40:41.336 --> 01:40:43.905
I WAS A PIG.
I WAS A PIG.

01:40:43.905 --> 01:40:46.040
IT'S ALL RIGHT.
LISTEN.

01:40:47.309 --> 01:40:50.212
DO NOT DROP ANCHOR HERE.

01:40:50.212 --> 01:40:52.347
UNDERSTAND ?

01:41:05.527 --> 01:41:08.863
[ Susanna Narrating ]
WHEN YOU DON'T WANT TO FEEL,

01:41:08.863 --> 01:41:12.867
DEATH CAN SEEM LIKE A DREAM.

01:41:12.867 --> 01:41:15.803
BUT SEEING DEATH--

01:41:15.803 --> 01:41:18.406
REALLY SEEING IT--

01:41:18.406 --> 01:41:21.643
MAKES DREAMING ABOUT IT
FUCKING RIDICULOUS.

01:41:23.545 --> 01:41:27.282
MAYBE THERE'S A MOMENT
GROWING UP...

01:41:27.282 --> 01:41:29.684
WHEN SOMETHING PEELS BACK.

01:41:29.684 --> 01:41:31.686
MAYBE.
MAYBE I--

01:41:31.686 --> 01:41:36.524
WE LOOK FOR SECRETS BECAUSE
WE CAN'T BELIEVE OUR MINDS--
AND THOUGH I MISSED LISA,

01:41:36.524 --> 01:41:38.360
LIFE WAS EASIER WITHOUT HER.

01:41:38.360 --> 01:41:42.964
A THOUGHT IS A HARD THING
TO CONTROL--
OUT IN THE REAL WORLD--

01:41:42.964 --> 01:41:45.567
ALL I KNOW IS THAT I BEGAN
TO FEEL THINGS AGAIN--

01:41:45.567 --> 01:41:48.836
...CRAZY, SANE,
STUPID, SMART, ANGRY--
...WHATEVER I WAS--

01:41:48.836 --> 01:41:52.174
I KNEW THERE WAS ONLY ONE WAY
BACK TO THE WORLD,

01:41:52.174 --> 01:41:54.509
AND THAT WAS TO USE THE PLACE--

01:41:54.509 --> 01:41:56.978
TO TALK.

01:41:56.978 --> 01:42:01.316
[ Indistinct ]
SO I SAW THE GREAT AND WONDERFL
DR. WICK THREE TIMES A WEEK,

01:42:01.316 --> 01:42:04.352
AND I LET HER HEAR
EVERY THOUGHT IN MY HEAD.

01:42:07.889 --> 01:42:11.993
DO YOU THINK MAYBE
I HAVE E.S.P. OR SOMETHING ?
THAT I'M GIFTED ?

01:42:11.993 --> 01:42:14.529
PERHAPS.

01:42:26.508 --> 01:42:29.344
YOU THINK I CAN BE HOME
BY THANKSGIVING ?

01:42:33.248 --> 01:42:36.284
NOTHING HAS HAPPENED
IN WEEKS, YOU KNOW.

01:42:36.284 --> 01:42:39.721
THE POINT IS CONTROL.

01:42:39.721 --> 01:42:41.756
YEAH, AND HERE I AM--

01:42:41.756 --> 01:42:44.125
IN CONTROL, OFF MEDS,

01:42:44.125 --> 01:42:46.928
NO HEADACHES, SLEEPING SOUND.

01:42:55.337 --> 01:42:58.072
[ Woman On TV ]
OH, WILL YOU HELP ME ?
CAN YOU HELP ME ?

01:42:58.072 --> 01:43:00.275
[ Woman 2 ]
YOU DON'T NEED TO BE
HELPED ANY LONGER.

01:43:00.275 --> 01:43:02.777
YOU'VE ALWAYS HAD THE POWER
TO GO BACK TO KANSAS.

01:43:02.777 --> 01:43:06.414
I HAVE ?
[ Man ]
THEN WHY DIDN'T YOU
TELL HER BEFORE ?

01:43:06.414 --> 01:43:10.485
BECAUSE SHE WOULDN'T HAVE
BELIEVED ME. SHE HAD
TO LEARN IT FOR HERSELF.

01:43:10.485 --> 01:43:13.087
[ Man ]
WHAT HAVE YOU
LEARNED, DOROTHY ?

01:43:13.087 --> 01:43:14.956
[ Dorothy ]
WELL,

01:43:17.625 --> 01:43:20.362
I THINK THAT IT--
THAT IT WASN'T ENOUGH

01:43:20.362 --> 01:43:23.164
JUST TO WANT TO SEE
UNCLE HENRY AND AUNTIE EM.

01:43:23.164 --> 01:43:26.401
[ Woman ]
VALERIE.
AND THAT IF I EVER GO LOOKING

01:43:26.401 --> 01:43:28.503
[ Whispering ]
FOR MY HEART'S DESIRE AGAIN,

01:43:28.503 --> 01:43:32.240
I WON'T LOOK ANY FURTHER
THAN MY OWN BACK YARD.

01:43:32.240 --> 01:43:34.642
BECAUSE IF IT ISN'T THERE,

01:43:34.642 --> 01:43:36.978
I NEVER REALLY LOST IT
TO BEGIN WITH.

01:43:36.978 --> 01:43:38.980
IS THAT RIGHT ?

01:43:38.980 --> 01:43:40.915
[ TV Continues, Indistinct ]

01:44:02.203 --> 01:44:04.439
[ Gretta ]
THANKS, JOE.

01:44:55.089 --> 01:44:57.024
[ Tapping ]

01:45:06.634 --> 01:45:08.436
GO AWAY.

01:45:08.436 --> 01:45:10.572
GO AWAY !

01:45:11.906 --> 01:45:13.841
LISA.

01:45:16.644 --> 01:45:18.580
IT'S ME.

01:45:32.927 --> 01:45:37.064
IT'S BEEN A WHILE...

01:45:37.064 --> 01:45:39.734
AND I JUST WANTED TO SAY HEY.

01:45:43.805 --> 01:45:46.941
YOU OKAY ?

01:45:46.941 --> 01:45:49.343
FABULOUS.

01:45:49.343 --> 01:45:51.278
[ Valerie ]
SUSANNA.

01:45:51.278 --> 01:45:54.682
YOU'RE GOING TO BE LATE.
GRETTA'S WAITING FOR YOU.

01:45:54.682 --> 01:45:56.618
OKAY.

01:45:58.820 --> 01:46:00.822
I GOT TO GO.

01:46:00.822 --> 01:46:02.824
DOCTOR WICK.

01:46:04.692 --> 01:46:07.429
ARE THEY STILL
FUCKING WITH YOU ?

01:46:10.432 --> 01:46:12.567
THEY'RE, UH--

01:46:13.568 --> 01:46:16.704
ACTUALLY,
THEY'RE LETTING ME OUT.

01:46:20.174 --> 01:46:22.109
OH, THAT'S GREAT.

01:46:25.046 --> 01:46:27.582
YOU BETTER GO.

01:46:43.097 --> 01:46:47.669
UH, WELL, MY DAD GOT ME A JOB--
A PART-TIME JOB--

01:46:47.669 --> 01:46:50.071
AT A BOOKSTORE
IN HARVARD SQUARE.

01:46:50.071 --> 01:46:53.541
AND I GOT AN APARTMENT
WITH A PHONE SO I CAN--

01:46:53.541 --> 01:46:55.677
STAY IN TOUCH.
UH-HUH.

01:46:56.744 --> 01:46:59.481
YEP.
AND, UH,
I'LL BE SEEING SONIA...

01:46:59.481 --> 01:47:01.282
TWICE A WEEK.

01:47:01.282 --> 01:47:05.419
IS THAT YOUR LONG-TERM
PLAN, TO WORK IN RETAIL ?

01:47:08.923 --> 01:47:11.425
MY PLAN ?
NO.

01:47:11.425 --> 01:47:14.562
THEN WHAT DO YOU PLAN TO DO ?

01:47:16.063 --> 01:47:18.600
I PLAN TO WRITE.

01:47:19.801 --> 01:47:21.969
AH.

01:47:26.007 --> 01:47:28.209
[ McWilley ]
POLLY CLARK.

01:47:28.209 --> 01:47:31.145
CYNTHIA CROWLEY.

01:47:34.348 --> 01:47:36.718
SUSANNA KAYSEN.

01:47:38.553 --> 01:47:41.288
YOU KNOW WHAT ?
I DON'T THINK I NEED THEM.
SLEEPING PILLS, DARLING.

01:47:41.288 --> 01:47:43.625
I--
YOU WANT TO BE RESTED
FOR TOMORROW, DON'T YOU ?

01:47:43.625 --> 01:47:46.193
THE LAST NIGHT IS
A LONG ONE. GOOD GIRL.

01:47:46.193 --> 01:47:48.195
KATIE COOPER.

01:47:48.195 --> 01:47:49.997
[ Woman Shouting ]

01:47:49.997 --> 01:47:52.133
[ McWilley ]
ROSEMARY JONES.

01:47:54.401 --> 01:47:57.539
TERESA McCULLIAN.

01:48:05.179 --> 01:48:08.115
[ Shouting, Clamoring ]

01:48:13.320 --> 01:48:15.857
[ Shouting, Shrieking ]

01:48:20.595 --> 01:48:22.730
[ Shrieking ]

01:48:27.735 --> 01:48:29.871
[ Clamoring Continues ]

01:49:21.889 --> 01:49:24.558
RUBY ?

01:49:35.302 --> 01:49:37.238
[ Cat Meows ]

01:49:42.309 --> 01:49:44.245
RUBY ?

01:49:47.048 --> 01:49:48.850
RUBY--

01:49:48.850 --> 01:49:50.985
[ Woman Speaking, Indistinct ]

01:50:04.265 --> 01:50:07.401
[ Lisa ]
"IF I SPREAD MY FINGERS OUT,
MY HAND LOOKED MORE HUMAN.

01:50:07.401 --> 01:50:09.403
"SO I DID THAT.

01:50:09.403 --> 01:50:12.139
"BUT IT WASN'T TIRING
HOLDING MY FINGERS APART,
SO I LET THEM RELAX.

01:50:12.139 --> 01:50:15.009
"AND THEN I TURNED MY HAND
OVER.

01:50:15.009 --> 01:50:17.344
OH, MY GOD.
"THE BACK OF IT
WASN'T MUCH BETTER.

01:50:17.344 --> 01:50:19.747
MY VEINS BULGED."

01:50:19.747 --> 01:50:22.016
[ Continues, Indistinct ]

01:50:24.051 --> 01:50:27.621
SHUT UP. I'M READING.
SHUT UP.

01:50:27.621 --> 01:50:29.423
LISA !

01:50:29.423 --> 01:50:34.095
"I CAN HONESTLY SAY THAT MY
MEMORY HAS BEEN TRANSFORMED...

01:50:34.095 --> 01:50:37.765
"SO THAT BY FREUD'S DEFINITION,
I HAVE ACHIEVED MENTAL HEALTH.
[ Chuckling ]

01:50:37.765 --> 01:50:40.534
AND MY DISCHARGE SHEET READS
'RECOVERED.'"

01:50:40.534 --> 01:50:43.037
OH.
"RECOVERED."
[ Laughing ]

01:50:45.506 --> 01:50:48.275
DON'T DO THIS !

01:50:48.275 --> 01:50:50.311
"WHATEVER IT WAS--"

01:50:51.946 --> 01:50:54.048
"HAD MY PERSONALITY--"
LISA !

01:50:54.048 --> 01:50:56.150
[ Continues, Indistinct ]

01:50:56.150 --> 01:50:59.520
"HAD I STOPPED ARGUING ?"
[ Laughs ]
LISA !

01:50:59.520 --> 01:51:01.723
[ Lisa ]
"RECOVERED."

01:51:01.723 --> 01:51:04.792
HEY, SUSANNA.
WE WERE JUST READING YOUR BOOK.
WE FIGURED ON YOUR LAST NIGHT

01:51:04.792 --> 01:51:07.128
WE'D HAVE A LITTLE SALON--
A LITTLE READ-ALOUD.

01:51:07.128 --> 01:51:09.731
CELEBRATE ALL THE WISDOM
YOU'RE CARRYING INTO THE WORLD.

01:51:09.731 --> 01:51:12.900
TRY TO LEARN SOMETHING--
GROW AS PEOPLE.

01:51:12.900 --> 01:51:17.038
WE READ HOW
WHEN YOU WERE A BABY,
THEY STRAPPED YOU TO A BOARD.

01:51:17.038 --> 01:51:19.040
AND HOW YOU THINK GEORGINA
DOESN'T REALLY WANT TO LEAVE,

01:51:19.040 --> 01:51:21.675
AND POLLY NEVER WILL,
AND THAT I'M CRIMINALLY INSANE.

01:51:21.675 --> 01:51:24.311
WHAT--
WHAT ARE YOU GUYS DOING HERE ?

01:51:24.311 --> 01:51:28.015
"LISA'S EYES, ONCE SO MAGNETIC,
NOW JUST LOOK EMPTY."

01:51:28.015 --> 01:51:30.217
[ Whispering ]
LISA.

01:51:30.217 --> 01:51:32.820
THAT IS MINE.

01:51:32.820 --> 01:51:35.156
THAT IS MINE.

01:51:35.156 --> 01:51:39.460
GEORGINA.
"GEORGINA LIES ONLY
TO PEOPLE WHO KEEP HER HERE.

01:51:39.460 --> 01:51:42.296
SOMETIMES I THINK
SHE WANTS TO LIVE
IN OZ FOREVER."

01:51:42.296 --> 01:51:44.298
[ Lisa ]
HOW PERCEPTIVE.
YOU BETTER ERASE THAT THING.

01:51:44.298 --> 01:51:46.267
GEORGINA, I--
YOU BETTER ERASE IT !

01:51:46.267 --> 01:51:48.335
'CAUSE MY FATHER
IS THE HEAD OF THE C.I.A.,

01:51:48.335 --> 01:51:50.537
AND HE COULD
HAVE YOU DEAD IN MINUTES !

01:51:50.537 --> 01:51:52.639
- "IN THIS WORLD,
LOOKS ARE EVERYTHING.
- [Susanna ] OH, GOD.

01:51:52.639 --> 01:51:56.778
"SOMETIMES I THINK
POLLY'S SWEETNESS AND PURITY
AREN'T GENUINE AT ALL,

01:51:56.778 --> 01:52:00.247
BUT A DESPERATE ATTEMPT
TO MAKE IT EASIER
FOR US TO LOOK AT HER."

01:52:00.247 --> 01:52:04.018
SO NICE OF YOU
TO PASS JUDGMENT ON US
NOW THAT YOU'RE CURED.

01:52:04.018 --> 01:52:06.520
WHAT THE FUCK
ARE YOU DOING, LISA ?

01:52:06.520 --> 01:52:09.456
I'M PLAYING THE VILLAIN, BABY.
JUST LIKE YOU WANT.

01:52:09.456 --> 01:52:12.259
I TRY TO GIVE YOU
EVERYTHING YOU WANT.
NO, YOU DON'T.

01:52:13.761 --> 01:52:15.863
YOU WANTED YOUR FILE--
I FOUND YOU YOUR FILE.
YOU WANTED OUT--

01:52:15.863 --> 01:52:18.866
I GOT YOU OUT.
YOU NEEDED MONEY--
I FOUND YOU SOME.

01:52:18.866 --> 01:52:22.603
I'M CONSISTENT.
I TOLD YOU THE TRUTH.
I DIDN'T WRITE IT IN A BOOK.

01:52:22.603 --> 01:52:24.806
I TOLD YOU TO YOUR FACE.

01:52:24.806 --> 01:52:26.607
AND I TOLD DAISY TO HER FACE--

01:52:26.607 --> 01:52:29.010
WHAT EVERYBODY KNEW
AND WOULDN'T SAY--
AND SHE KILLED HERSELF.

01:52:29.010 --> 01:52:31.012
AND I PLAYED
THE FUCKING VILLAIN.

