THAT I'M A FUCKING WHORE ?

01:54:17.451 --> 01:54:19.921
OR THAT MY PARENTS
WISH I WERE DEAD ?

01:54:19.921 --> 01:54:23.257
BECAUSE YOU'RE
DEAD ALREADY, LISA.

01:54:29.130 --> 01:54:33.800
NO ONE CARES IF YOU DIE, LISA.

01:54:33.800 --> 01:54:37.071
BECAUSE YOU'RE DEAD ALREADY.

01:54:37.071 --> 01:54:41.208
YOUR HEART IS COLD.

01:54:43.077 --> 01:54:45.612
THAT'S WHY YOU KEEP
COMING BACK HERE.

01:54:47.081 --> 01:54:50.084
YOU'RE NOT FREE.

01:54:50.084 --> 01:54:53.087
YOU NEED THIS PLACE.
YOU NEED IT TO FEEL ALIVE.

01:54:53.087 --> 01:54:55.156
IT'S PATHETIC.

01:54:55.156 --> 01:54:57.524
[ Screams ]
[ Glass Breaking ]

01:54:59.160 --> 01:55:02.997
[ Sobbing ]
GOD.

01:55:05.766 --> 01:55:08.970
[ Sobbing ]
I HATE--

01:55:23.017 --> 01:55:26.153
[ Wailing ]

01:55:36.897 --> 01:55:40.567
I'VE WASTED A YEAR OF MY LIFE.

01:55:45.306 --> 01:55:48.709
MAYBE EVERYONE
OUT THERE IS A LIAR,

01:55:52.046 --> 01:55:55.149
AND MAYBE THE WHOLE WORLD...

01:55:55.149 --> 01:55:58.585
IS STUPID AND IGNORANT,

01:56:01.822 --> 01:56:04.525
BUT I'D RATHER BE IN IT--

01:56:05.993 --> 01:56:09.997
I'D RATHER BE FUCKING IN IT--

01:56:09.997 --> 01:56:12.533
THAN DOWN HERE WITH YOU.

01:56:27.148 --> 01:56:30.684
[ Georgina ]
LISA.

01:56:30.684 --> 01:56:33.954
DON'T.

01:56:33.954 --> 01:56:36.157
DON'T.

01:56:43.630 --> 01:56:47.034
[ Sobs ]

01:56:47.034 --> 01:56:49.203
OH, GOD.

01:57:32.879 --> 01:57:34.815
DID YOU GET IT ?

01:57:37.951 --> 01:57:41.488
