WITH A TRANSVESTITE
IN THE MEN'S WARD.

01:57:43.890 --> 01:57:46.093
THANKS.

01:58:41.982 --> 01:58:44.851
[ Whispering ]
YOU KNOW,

01:58:44.851 --> 01:58:46.887
I'M NOT REALLY DEAD.

01:58:52.993 --> 01:58:55.128
I KNOW.

01:58:57.598 --> 01:58:59.400
[ Sighs ]

01:58:59.400 --> 01:59:01.868
I'M GOING TO MISS YOU,
SUSIE Q.

01:59:03.937 --> 01:59:05.739
NO, YOU'RE NOT.

01:59:05.739 --> 01:59:08.074
