TO COME AND SEE ME.

01:59:10.844 --> 01:59:13.747
OKAY ?

01:59:13.747 --> 01:59:17.618
[ Sighs ]

01:59:17.618 --> 01:59:20.221
YEAH.

01:59:20.221 --> 01:59:22.423
[ Chattering ]

01:59:32.799 --> 01:59:35.302
HEY, GEORGINA.

01:59:35.302 --> 01:59:38.439
YOU KNOW ALL THAT STUFF
I WRITE IN MY JOURNAL ?

01:59:38.439 --> 01:59:40.974
I DON'T KNOW WHAT I'M SAYING.

01:59:40.974 --> 01:59:44.945
THEY'RE JUST THOUGHTS.

01:59:44.945 --> 01:59:48.181
MAYBE I'M THE LIAR.

01:59:48.181 --> 01:59:51.418
MAYBE NOT.

01:59:59.793 --> 02:00:01.728
SEE YOU.

02:00:09.836 --> 02:00:11.638
POLLY,

02:00:11.638 --> 02:00:14.475
DO YOU THINK
IF I LEFT RUBY HERE,

02:00:14.475 --> 02:00:16.510
YOU'D TAKE CARE
OF HER FOR ME ?

02:00:16.510 --> 02:00:20.814
AND LET ME PLAY WITH HER
WHEN I COME FOR MY THERAPY ?

02:00:20.814 --> 02:00:23.216
[ Chuckling ]

02:00:23.216 --> 02:00:26.086
YEAH. OKAY.

02:00:26.086 --> 02:00:28.221
THANK YOU.

02:00:30.223 --> 02:00:32.893
BYE, RUBY.

02:00:36.430 --> 02:00:39.800
BYE.
YEAH.

02:00:54.247 --> 02:00:56.817
REMEMBER ME WHEN
YOU SHAVE YOUR LEGS.

02:01:26.847 --> 02:01:29.450
[ Susanna Narrating ]
DECLARED HEALTHY...

02:01:29.450 --> 02:01:32.586
AND SENT BACK INTO THE WORLD.

02:01:32.586 --> 02:01:35.456
